{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Permissions","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions\"><code>Permissions</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions/query\"><code>query()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions/revoke\"><code>revoke()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Permissions API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/permissions\"><code>Navigator.permissions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PermissionStatus\"><code>PermissionStatus</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/permissions\"><code>WorkerNavigator.permissions</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The Permissions interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a> provides the core Permission API functionality, such as methods for querying and revoking permissions</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"permissions.query\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions/query\" title=\"Permissions.query()\"><code>Permissions.query()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns the user permission status for a given API.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"permissions.request\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>Permissions.request()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Requests permission to use a given API. This is not currently supported in any browser.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"permissions.requestall\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>Permissions.requestAll()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Requests permission to use a given set of APIs. This is not currently supported in any browser.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"permissions.revoke\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions/revoke\" title=\"Permissions.revoke()\"><code>Permissions.revoke()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Revokes the permission currently set on a given API.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>permissions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">' geolocation'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">result</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'granted'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">showLocalNewsWithGeolocation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'prompt'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">showButtonToEnableLocalNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Don't do anything if the permission was denied.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/permissions/#permissions-interface","title":"Permissions"}],"query":"api.Permissions"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Support","id":"browser_support","isH3":false,"query":"api.Permissions","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser Support","id":"browser_support"}],"summary":"The Permissions interface of the Permissions API provides the core Permission API functionality, such as methods for querying and revoking permissions","popularity":0.001,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:17:24.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Permissions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Permissions","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/permissions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/permissions/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/4b4638246aad5d39b9a2e5c572b179b4c39c0a84","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions","title":"Permissions"}],"pageTitle":"Permissions - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}